description:

Inspired by my dad turning 61 today…& the stress of time passing & me still being in the place/situation that I’m in..30 years old..unemployed due to chronic pain & disabling anxiety that keeps me from socializing & being able to step outside of my room. I just want to be able to live comfortably so that my parents can grow older comfortably and hopefully be able to give back to them.
Daily digital abstract using photoshop.
